				<p rend="This is a fragment of a news clipping.  There are notes &#40;not in English&#41; in both margins."></p>
				<p><add>&#63;</add> wives Jewesses&#44; or at least let the children be circumcised and<lb/> stay with their fathers&#63;  Surely for no &#761;other reason than this<lb/> that <persName>Ezra</persName> did not want to disgrace the nation by making such<lb/> proselytes &#124; and sport with the holy &#763;Word of God&#44; and make by&#45;<lb/>ways and side&#45;doors to the sacred edifice of our holy religion&#44;<lb/> that every one may smuggle <del>himself</del> in and out whatever he<lb/> pleases&#44; and thus suit every one&#39;s way of thinking&#44; as <persName>Iben Ezra</persName><lb/> to <persName>Ezra</persName> &#124; vi. explains&#44; <add>Hebrew</add>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Hoping that this may cause our people to change their<lb/> opinion concerning proselytes&#44; I remain&#44; dear sir&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Most respectfully yours&#44;</p>
				<p><persName role="author">Dr. Illowy</persName>.</p>
				<p>Finf&#252;ger&#58; <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>&#44; <date>January 19&#44; 1865</date></p>
